@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}
<main aria-labelledby="title">
    <h2 id="title">@ViewBag.Title WalletWise</h2>
    <h4 class="text-primary">@ViewBag.Message</h4>
    <p>Your reliable companion in managing your finances with ease and efficiency. Whether you're tracking expenses, monitoring income, or managing your savings, our app is designed to empower you with the tools you need to take control of your financial future.</p>

    <div class="card my-4">
        <h4 class="card-header">Our Mission</h4>
        <p class="card-body">
            We believe that managing personal finances should be simple, accessible, and stress-free. Our mission is to provide you with a comprehensive platform that simplifies financial management, helping you make informed decisions and achieve your financial goals.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card my-4">
        <h4 class="card-header">Key Features</h4>
        <div class="row gap-5 justify-content-center card-body">
            <section class="col-md-3 card shadow" aria-labelledby="feature1">
                <h2 class="card-header text-center" id="feature1">Expense Tracking</h2>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>
                        Easily record and categorize your expenses to keep track of where your money is going.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Add and edit expense entries with details like amount, date, and category.</li>
                            <li>Attach receipts or notes to each expense for better tracking.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="col-md-3 card shadow" aria-labelledby="feature2">
                <h2 class="card-header text-center" id="feature2">Income Tracking</h2>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>
                        Keep track of all your sources of income to get a clear picture of your financial situation.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Record income entries with details such as source, amount, and date.</li>
                            <li>View and analyze income trends over time.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="col-md-3 card shadow" aria-labelledby="feature3">
                <h2 class="card-header text-center" id="feature3">Budget Management</h2>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>
                        Set and manage budgets for different categories to stay within your financial limits.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Create budgets for various expense categories (e.g., groceries, entertainment).</li>
                            <li>Monitor your spending against your budget and get notifications when nearing limits.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="col-md-3 card shadow" aria-labelledby="feature4">
                <h2 class="card-header text-center" id="feature4">Financial Reports</h2>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>
                        Generate detailed reports to analyze your financial health and track progress towards your goals.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Create and view reports such as expense summaries, income statements, and budget vs. actuals.</li>
                            <li>Export reports to PDF or Excel for sharing and offline analysis.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="col-md-3 card shadow" aria-labelledby="feature5">
                <h2 class="card-header text-center" id="feature5">Customizable Categories</h2>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>
                        Tailor categories to fit your personal financial situation for better organization and tracking.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Add, edit, or delete expense and income categories as needed.</li>
                            <li>Use predefined or custom categories to classify your financial transactions.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="col-md-3 card shadow" aria-labelledby="feature6">
                <h2 class="card-header text-center" id="feature6">Goal Setting</h2>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>
                        Set financial goals and track your progress towards achieving them.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Define short-term and long-term financial goals.</li>
                            <li>Monitor progress and receive reminders to stay on track.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card my-4">
        <h4 class="card-header">Why Choose WalletWise?</h4>
        <div class="accordion" id="accordionExample">
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                        User-Friendly Interface
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <strong>Our app is designed with simplicity in mind, making it easy for anyone to manage their finances, regardless of their financial expertise.</strong>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                        Comprehensive Features
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <strong>From tracking your expenses and income to managing budgets and generating reports, our app offers all the tools you need in one place.</strong>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                        Security First
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <strong>We prioritize the security of your financial data. Our platform employs advanced encryption and security measures to ensure that your information remains safe and confidential.</strong>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                        Personalized Experience
                    </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                    <div class="accordion-body">
                        <strong>Customize your financial management experience with categories and features tailored to your needs. Whether you’re saving for a big purchase or just trying to keep track of daily spending, we’ve got you covered.</strong>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card my-4">
        <h4 class="card-header">Join Our Community</h4>
        <p class="card-body">
            At <b>WalletWise</b>, a Personal Finance Manager, we’re more than just a financial tool – we’re a community of individuals striving for financial well-being. Join us today and start taking control of your financial journey.
        </p>
    </div>

</main>